{"article_id":"qSAo9eWZXm4R9Zij","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"MGM Resorts International has filed a lawsuit in federal court against more than 1,000 victims of last October 's shooting massacre","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"claiming","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"it is not financially liable for the tragedy .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"The massacre occurred on the night of Oct. 1 during a country music festival on the Las Vegas strip .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"The perpetrator ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"firing from the window of the Mandalay Bay Resort and Casino ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"murdered 58 people","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and shot more than 400 others .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"In total , there were more than 800 victims .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"MGM Resorts owns Mandalay Bay .","depth":3},{"id":10,"text":"The suit ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"which was filed in court last Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"claims","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that suits against MGM","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"relating to the massacre","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"`` must be dismissed ''","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"because MGM has `` no liability of any kind to defendants , ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"the Las Vegas Review-Journal reported .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The newspaper explained :","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"The company cites a 2002 federal act","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that extends liability protection to any company","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"that uses \" anti-terrorism \" technology or services","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"that can \" help prevent and respond to mass violence. \"","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"In this case ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"the company argues ,","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"the security vendor","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"MGM hired for Route 91 ,","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"Contemporary Services Corp. ,","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"was protected from liability","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"because its services had been certified by the Department of Homeland Security","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"for \" protecting against and responding to acts of mass injury and destruction . \"","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"Because MGM hired the security company for the Route 91 country music festival ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"the protection extends to MGM ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"the lawsuit argues .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"MGM does not seek damages against the massacre victims .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Instead , its filing only asks a judge to consider","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"whether the 2002 law extends its protections to MGM ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"if so ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"to disallow future civil litigation against MGM","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"relating to the tragedy .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Debra DeShong , a spokesperson for MGM , said","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"MGM 's filing will provide a `` timely '' resolution for victims .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"`` Years of drawn out litigation and hearings are not in the best interest of victims , the community and those","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"still healing , ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"she said ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"according to the Review-Journal .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"The filing comes","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"after more than 450 victims and their families filed a lawsuit against a number of entities ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"including MGM and the killer 's estate ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"last November .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"The suit claimed","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"MGM is negligent in the shooting","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"because :","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"MGM failed to properly monitor the Mandalay Bay ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"including who was entering and leaving the premises .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"MGM failed to properly respond to the killer","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"shooting a casino security guard .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"MGM failed to take adequate precautions against a potential killer","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"stockpiling weapons and ammunition .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"The killer ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"who had VIP status with MGM ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"was allowed to use a service elevator .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"MGM failed to properly train employees how to identify suspicious behavior .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Las Vegas lawyer Robert Eglet , an attorney","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"representing many of the Vegas victims ,","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"blasted MGM 's decision","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"to file their suit in the federal court system .","depth":4},{"id":68,"text":"He characterized the action as a `` blatant display of judge shopping ''","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"that `` verges on unethical . ''","depth":4},{"id":70,"text":"`` I ' ve never seen a more outrageous thing ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"where they sue the victims","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"in an effort","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"to find a judge","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"they like .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"It ' s just really sad that they would stoop to this level , ''","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"he told the Review-Journal .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":140,"right":152,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":86,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":85,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":79,"right":84,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":0,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":84,"left":3,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":82,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":